{"tid":2162382,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食評]黃店口水雞","createTime":"2020-08-18T05:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T05:59:51.000Z","uid":310468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a83ed94ce8e2b4e24cbeee47c201c6350826fabb","tid":2162382,"uid":310468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wn1JOEH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwn1JOEH.jpg&h=94ae838e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我一直都好鐘意食呢間黃店嘅口水雞<br />\n首先夠麻夠香夠辣，有好多蒜頭，好重花椒味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鹹味都好啱，唔會話鹹到飛起。啲雞都好滑，唔會話俾啲雞胸肉黎俾你食。仲要都幾多下。個底仲有拍黃瓜，好爽脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，上次食啲黃瓜就鹹咗啲，今次就啱啱好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲雞係凍食嘅，夏天食就一流，好餸飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有機會去西九龍中心可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n間鋪係喺西九龍8樓，個名係89<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有連儂墻(依家只剩下少量)"}]}